		<li>Natural resistance to rot and insects reduces buyer concerns</li>
		<li>Can be stained to match home exterior perfectly</li>
		<li>Environmentally friendly material appeals to green-minded buyers</li>
	</ul>

	<p><strong>Value-maximizing choices:</strong></p>
	<ul>
