		<li><strong>Style:</strong> Vertical board-on-board or shadowbox design</li>
		<li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Professionally sealed before listing (critical!)</li>
		<li><strong>Height:</strong> 6 feet standard (matches neighborhood expectations)</li>
		<li><strong>Posts:</strong> Cedar posts (not pressure-treated) for consistent appearance</li>
	</ul>

	<p><strong>Typical value added:</strong> $5,000-8,500 on homes valued $300,000-500,000</p>

